longBusinessSummary: Combine Will International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates as an original design manufacturer, original equipment manufacturer, and supplier of corporate premiums, toys, and consumer products. The company manufactures and trades in plastic toys, die castings, and electronics parts, as well as premium items. It operates in the People's Republic of China, Hong Kong, Macau, Taiwan, Germany, Switzerland, and internationally. The company was founded in 1992 and is based in Tai Po, Hong Kong. Combine Will International Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Raffles Nominees (Pte.) Ltd.
